import React from "react";
import * as S from "styled-components";

const MovieDetailPage = () => {
    return (
        <MovieDetailContainer>
            <PosterContainer>
                <Poster src="movie-poster.jpg" alt="Movie Poster" />
            </PosterContainer>
            <MovieDetails>
                <Title>Movie Title</Title>
                <GenreList>
                    <Genre>Genre 1</Genre>
                    <Genre>Genre 2</Genre>
                </GenreList>
                <Synopsis>
                    Movie synopsis goes here. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet,
                    consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed auctor, magna a bibendum
                    bibendum, augue magna tincidunt enim, eget ultricies magna
                    augue eget lorem.
                </Synopsis>
                <Credits>
                    <CreditItem>Actor 1</CreditItem>
                    <CreditItem>Actor 2</CreditItem>
                    <CreditItem>Actor 3</CreditItem>
                </Credits>
                <ReleaseDate>Release Date: YYYY-MM-DD</ReleaseDate>
                <ReviewContainer>
                    <ReviewTitle>Reviews</ReviewTitle>
                    <ReviewList>
                        <ReviewItem>Review 1</ReviewItem>
                        <ReviewItem>Review 2</ReviewItem>
                        <ReviewItem>Review 3</ReviewItem>
                    </ReviewList>
                    <ExpandReviewsButton>More Reviews</ExpandReviewsButton>
                </ReviewContainer>
            </MovieDetails>
        </MovieDetailContainer>
    );
};
